There was a reportz spread about the world, that these three men were all the sons of one adulterous woman; who, when she came to die, refused to shew any repentance for her fault, because she had been the mother of such excellent and admired personS‚ as they all proved to be ; which she thought a sufficient recompense or excuse for her sin.
